prependContent.description: Content to put at the top of the file export. A 2D array of CsvCell objects (see [Prepending and Appending Content](#prepending-and-appending-content)). Alternatively, you can pass a multi-line string that is simply appended to the top of the file content.

appendContent.description: Content to put at the bottom of the file export. A 2D array of CsvCell objects (see [Prepending and Appending Content](#prepending-and-appending-content)). Alternatively, you can pass a multi-line string that is simply appended to the bottom of the file content.
